Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:53.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I heard a sullen, unusual\Nsound ring through the cold air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I hearing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:00.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.
