Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how long has this sickness affected the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been fourteen years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:21.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone looks fine but their skin\Nbecomes dreadfully hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they become unable to move their limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:29.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My long-time friends have the worst case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They can't even sit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are these friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The couple at the west end of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:44.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The townspeople all say that their daughter\Nis the cause of the sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her name is Shige.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:56.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since she was born, the people\Naround her became sick, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:00.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is the truth, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:06.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've tried for fourteen years to find the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige eventually stopped speaking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:13.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and now everyone is nothing but suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, that's all for this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:25.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving her so much pity just because\Nher parents are close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should give us all a raise instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, that's a big hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't have any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:54.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The people here never get sick of it, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you say something to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That rumor is just crap, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it were true,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:10.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's not like you got your friends\Nand family sick on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My village too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:19.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost half of my friends and family\Nafter the storm a couple of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:24.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I decided I'd stay here and make\Nmoney in my dad's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You decided you've got no other choice too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you're doing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you another doc the Boss hired?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything. She won't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tetsu! Get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see the "rust", don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:50.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name's Ginko. I was called here to treat the sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to hound you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can cure the sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can talk in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to rust myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:17.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:25.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see the rust too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:28.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:32.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My voice is terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:36.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was nothing you'd expect from her small body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A deep, cracked voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:46.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My voice became like this after\NI kept screaming in that cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:51.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But with a bittersweet ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter how much my voice changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:01.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It still makes rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:04.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a mind boggling voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:26.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever I spoke, rust grew on everything\Nand everyone around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was normal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:34.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shige, sing a song for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:40.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd even sing my favorite songs\Nfor everyone unsuspectingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:45.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no one else saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:51.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only realized that it was a bad thing when I was four –
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,everyone started becoming crippled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:58.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told my parents about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige, don't tell {\i1}anyone{\i0} what you just told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have no place here if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:15.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're only getting by because\Nthe village chief is kind to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:23.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Live by cheating on everyone. Buying pity from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:27.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until some day we can pay them back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:31.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,don't ever speak, Shige.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't said a word to anyone since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:42.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been ten years since I've spoken to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not their fault that everyone hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:50.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I chose to survive with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The more I hear, the stranger it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:59.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you make such a voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:04.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's mixed with the sound of a pitch\Nthat no human could produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:08.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might sound a bit different to yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:11.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there's a sound that bears a close\Nresemblance to your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a Mushi called "Yasabi", and it's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:24.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some can see it, some can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a being of a different existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:32.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yasabi are normally harmless creatures\Nthat decompose dead things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when they do, they emit a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:39.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your voice is like that sound,\Na few hundred times louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:44.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you speak, Yasabi from all throughout\Nthe mountains gather expecting food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there's nothing to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably why they're attaching\Nto the living as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, we just need to scatter them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:01.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then we may be able to get your voice back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not exactly a picky eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The whole place is rust colored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up? It's cold here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:41.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:46.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, aren't you afraid of Shige?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only been two years since I came to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:54.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't get the feeling that Shige\Nis the cause of the sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:55.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that why there isn't a single Yasabi on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:41.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If my voice comes back and I can speak again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can say thank you to Tetsu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can say it with my own voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:52.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:56.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll use your voice to rid the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:01.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you won't be safe living here after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:08.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can fix the sickness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:16.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I want to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:20.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teach me how to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, a facecloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:33.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Shige?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was all just a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll read it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:04.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You'll get sick if I spoke to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for everything. Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tetsu, who wrote this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:12.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:18.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, you seemed to have sympathy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do that, Tetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you and goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and clean the furnace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:42.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Shige. She's not getting away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:48.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run somewhere, Shige.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what they'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:07.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ginko-san hasn't told me how to rid the Mushi yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait over at that mountain pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:18.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll persuade everyone and then\Ntell you how to rid the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stay in this town either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That pass is in the same direction as my home village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She can't be safe alo–
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can do it, right, Shige?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san! Why are you defending Shige?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:46.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring Shige out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make her pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:54.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Banishing her won't cure the sickness. It's not her fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige was a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:01.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She spoke, laughed and sung like any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:06.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her voice just happened to have the\Nstuff to bring about the sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:13.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm saying, how is she supposed to apologize\Nto everyone who got sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:18.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been apologizing for the past ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:24.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she broke her pledge and spoke some bluffs,\Nno one would have been suspicious of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been paying for her crime the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean we can forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:34.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My child is her age, and she can't even walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, she will have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was her voice that brought the sickness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's her voice that can get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that enough to call it even?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:52.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone affected by the sickness\Nsuffered just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige, that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:08.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounded like you were leaving the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:12.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to do that once the sickness is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have anywhere to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come to my town then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've lost most of the houses and\Nships, but it's still a fishing village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're all chipping in to rebuild it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:55.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I scream from this distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we can cure the sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:50.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her unmistakable voice echoed\Nthroughout the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:09.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My legs feel lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Tetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:34.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got Tetsu-san sick too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's fine. He just lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:55.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:08.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you ended up doing pretty much just what\NI was going to tell you to do anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:13.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Echo your voice across the neighboring mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and scatter all the Yasabi that gathered in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:24.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except it had to be there at that pass,\Nwhere the sea was right behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because Yasabi don't like saltiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:33.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rust at the edge of the village where the\Nsea breeze passed through wasn't Yasabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just normal rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:44.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tetsu never got sick probably because he was\Nraised by the sea, and he went home often.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:49.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, too, can live a normal life by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:53.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you only scattered a small portion of the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:58.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to keep it up for several years to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:03.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though, you might really lose your voice first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:09.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I vaguely remember –
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:17.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the village before there wasn't much rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:23.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I loved this village back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:28.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I can bring back the old village even just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:37.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And ever since the girl left the village,\Nthe sickness slowly ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:39.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shige.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:40.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:41.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:43.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:47.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even now, the villagers say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:56.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,they can hear the broken but strangely\Nbeautiful, familiar singing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:59.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,echo throughout the mountains.
