Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:37.98,next-title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(675.428,401.142)\fad(2000,0)\be1\frz15.16}The\NJourney\Nto the\NField\Nof Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Journey to the Field of Fire.
